Realty One Group At The Beach

data.description:
Craftsman style, One level Beach House located right by the Ocean and Whale Coves. Zoned C-1 allows for STR Vacation Rental, Full time living or Both.  
 Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and pine beams, 3 BR  2 Full baths OFFICE and LNDRY room. 
  Chef's kitchen with pantry, granite counters, heated travertine tile floors, gas fireplace with rock accents, bamboo floors in the great room, solid pine trim and doors, cedar roof and siding.  Double car garage with side entry door, gas furnace and fenced back yard. Peekaboo view.         
  Walk to the Ocean for Whale watching and downtown to the rock wall for sightseeing, shopping and food enjoy the park, marina and boat doc for fun. 
Depoe bay has plenty of permeant benches all over the area for Whale watching,
